5. Find Total Sales for Each Customer

Incorrect Code
SELECT customer_id, SUM(amount) 
FROM sales;

Problem
SUM(amount) is an aggregate function
Need GROUP BY customer_id

Correct Code
SELECT customer_id, SUM(amount) AS total_sales
FROM sales
GROUP BY customer_id;

Result:

| customer_id | total_sales |
| ----------- | ----------- |
| 101         | 4500        |
| 102         | 5500        |
| 103         | 7000        |
| 104         | 3000        |
| 105         | 6000        |

===========








